<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ث ل ب:</span> <span class="c2">(ثَلَبَهُ)</span> صَرَّحَ بِالْعَيْبِ فِيهِ وَتَنَقَصَّهُ وَبَابُهُ ضَرَبَ. وَ <span class="c2">(الْمَثَالِبُ)</span> الْعُيُوبُ الْوَاحِدَةُ <span class="c2">(مَثْلَبَةٌ)</span> بِفَتْحِ اللَّامِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>